title: Is Sex a Priority
itunes:title: Is Sex a Priority
description:
1/28/19 - Today on the show we speaker and author Tony Gaskins stop by where he spoke about  his book "Make it Work", communication in relationships, and sex being a plus but not a priority. Moreover, we opened up the phone lines to see if any of our listeners agreed with him or believe that sex is a priority. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to journalist Tom Brokaw for his comments about Hispanics.
